The schematic connections

Conections for the Arduino code
BT- HC08 connections
  VCC-5V-From Reg.
  GND-From Reg.
  TX - D10 Arduino
  RX - D9 Arduino
Nano
  D10 - TX BLE
  D9 - RX BLE
  VCC-5V-From Reg.
  GND-From Reg.
  D4 - Relay Signal
Relay
  GND-From Reg.
  VCC-5V-From Reg.
  S (Signal)- D4 Arduino
  NO/NC- Load
Regulator 
  IN-12V In from supply
  GND- Common ground throughout the entire project
  OUT-5V out to components
